Text: "You won’t know what hit you if you don’t do what I say."
"You and your family won’t be safe unless you pay up."
"You’ll regret ignoring this warning. We’re watching you."
"If you don’t meet our demands, expect things to get very ugly."
"I have something on you that could ruin your life. Pay me, and I’ll keep quiet."
"If you don’t pay me by tomorrow, I’ll send your secrets to everyone you know."
"I have photos of you that would destroy your career. Do what I say, or I’ll release them."
"We have your loved one. If you ever want to see them again, follow our instructions."
"Your child is in our hands. Cooperate, or you won’t ever see them again."
"You have 24 hours to comply, or you’ll never hear from them again."
"One word from me, and your whole life will come crashing down."
"If you don’t do what we ask, everyone will know what you’ve done."
"I’ll make sure your entire career is ruined if you cross me."
"We know everything about you. Don’t test us."
"It would be wise to stop looking for a way out, because there isn’t one."
"You won’t get a second chance, so do exactly as we say."
"If you don’t pay, I’ll expose everything online for the world to see."
"Your data is already in our hands. A little money, and it stays private."
"I’ll destroy your online presence if you don’t cooperate right now."
"I know where you live. If you don't give me what I want, you’ll regret it."
"You’re not safe anymore. Your house is easy to find."
"One way or another, we’ll make you pay for what you’ve done."
"If you try to call the police, you’ll regret it. We’ll be there before they are."
"Don’t think about escaping. There’s no way out of this now."
"I told you what would happen if you didn’t pay. Now it’s too late."
"You’ve been warned. Now you’ll face the consequences."
"Anyone who crosses me doesn’t walk away from it. Trust me."
"You think this is over? It’s just beginning. I’ll make sure everyone knows what you’ve done."
"We have access to your bank accounts, your passwords. If you don’t do as we say, you’ll regret it."
"You have a choice: pay up, or we’ll make your life a living hell."
"We’ve got your dirty secrets. If you want to keep them hidden, you know what to do."
"If you don’t want the authorities to find out about your little secret, you better listen closely."
"Meet me tonight. The money needs to be in my hands by then, or this deal is off."
"I’ve already moved the cash. You’ll get your share once we make the transfer. No funny business."
"You better not screw up this deal, or I’ll find a way to make you disappear."
"You know what’s at stake. One wrong move, and we all go down."
"I’ve got connections who can get rid of the evidence. Just pay the fee and keep your mouth shut."
"You’re running out of time. Pay for the shipment, or you’ll be held responsible."
"I don’t care who you have to deal with. You get me the money, or we’ll take care of your problem another way."
"This is your final warning. I don’t want to see you again until you have the cash."
"We can either work together or against each other. Don’t make the wrong choice."
"You better have the product by the time I get there. If not, there will be consequences."
"This is a reminder: you owe us. Don’t make me come looking for you again."
"Our people are already watching you. Don’t think about crossing us."
"You didn’t think we’d forget, did you? Pay what you owe, or we’ll send someone to collect."
"You’ve been running from us for too long. It’s time to face the music."
"Stay out of our business, or we’ll make sure you regret it."
"You have exactly 24 hours to get us the money, or your store is going to burn down."
"We know where your safe is. If you don’t cooperate, we’ll take everything—and your family too."
"Your security won’t stop us. We’ll have what we need by the end of the night."
"You’ll regret locking that door. We always find a way in."
"You can’t stop us. We will strike when you least expect it."
"If you don’t change your policies, we’ll make sure the world knows what we’re capable of."
"Your government isn’t going to protect you. We can reach anyone, anywhere."
"If you don’t comply with our demands, we’ll make sure your city feels the consequences."
"Don’t try to run. You belong to us now."
"You’ll do as we say, or we’ll make things even worse for your family."
"We have your sister. If you want her back, you know what you need to do."
"You’re not in control anymore. You do what we say, or you’ll never see your loved ones again."
"You’re nothing but a pawn in our game. Don’t even think about escaping."
"We have access to all your accounts. Don’t think you can hide from us."
"Your data is in our hands. Pay us, or we’ll send everything to your boss."
"I can make your entire online life disappear in a flash. One wrong move and you’ll regret it."
"If you don’t transfer the money to our account, we’ll leak all your personal information."
"Your credit card numbers are already in our system. Pay now, or we’ll max them out."
"You’ll pay for this one way or another. I’ve got all your info, and you can’t stop me."
"Your identity isn’t yours anymore. It’s already in our hands, and you’ll pay the price."
"I’ll take what’s mine, whether you like it or not. You can’t stop what’s coming."
"You think your life is safe? Wait until I start making charges on your accounts."
"We have a reliable supply chain for top-quality heroin, cocaine, and meth. Are you ready to make a deal?"
"Limited-time offer: Buy 10 kilos of cocaine, get 2 free—act fast before prices go up!"
"Send the payment via this untraceable account, and we’ll launder it through a legitimate business."
"I’ve got what you need right now—cash only, no questions asked, meet me at the usual spot."
"You didn’t pay your debt—don’t make me come over there, it won’t end well for you."
"You didn’t listen to my warnings, now we’ll take care of business our way."
"You’re dealing with the right people now—pay up, or the consequences won’t be pretty."
"We’ve got the right connections to keep this quiet, just make sure you handle the payment upfront."
"Go to the hidden website, make your payment with Bitcoin, and your shipment will be delivered to your doorstep."
"If you don’t cooperate, we’ll release everything to the authorities, and you’ll never see freedom again."
"To finalize the transaction, send us your full name and shipping address, no one will know."
"Our boys are on the way to settle things. If you don’t want trouble, you better hand over what’s owed."
"I’ve got 100 kilos ready to go, we can make a big deal if you’re in—let’s talk numbers."
"We’ve got a secure route set up for transporting the goods, just give the green light and we’ll move."
"We can get you the best quality fentanyl, but you need to place your order before midnight to lock in the price."
"This is your private link to the dark web market where you can buy whatever you need, no trace, no records."
"We’ve got cops in our pocket—don’t worry about any interference, we control everything."
"We hit the jewelry store at 2 a.m. when the security guards are on break. The back door’s already unlocked."
"I’ll handle the surveillance cameras. You get the goods and meet me at the exit in five minutes. We’re in and out quick."
"No mess-ups. If the alarm goes off, we bail immediately."
"The shipment is scheduled for tonight, make sure the drop goes smoothly and no one gets caught."
"If anyone asks, the goods are coming from overseas, and we’ve paid off the right people."
"Get the package to the warehouse, don’t stop for anyone, and don’t trust anyone around you."
"The money’s already been moved through the account; just confirm the wire transfer and we’re set."
"We’ve got eyes on the target—everything’s in place for tomorrow, just stay quiet."
"Don’t worry, I’ve already paid off the cops. This is as clean as it gets."
"You didn’t follow through with the plan, now we’re coming to collect—no more chances."
"We need to hit the vault at midnight, make sure the cameras are disabled and the guards are distracted."
"They’re asking too many questions, make sure they stop talking, or we’ll have a problem."
"We’ve arranged everything on the inside—just make sure you don’t get caught up in the mess."
"The deal’s off unless you deliver the goods tonight, no excuses."
"Get rid of the evidence, make sure no one connects the dots."
"I’ve got people in place; you just need to make sure the shipment gets through customs."
"The cash is in a safe house—pick it up before anyone realizes it’s missing."
"If you want out, you’ll have to pay, and it’s not going to be cheap."
"You’re behind schedule; we’ll have to make an example of someone if you don’t deliver."
"Make sure the fingerprints are wiped off everything—leave no trace."
"The transfer’s been completed, but you need to move quickly before the authorities catch wind."
"You know the drill—if anyone asks, we’ve never met, and you don’t know anything."
"I’ll handle the inside job, but you need to make sure the perimeter is clear."
"This isn’t just about the money; if we don’t succeed, there’ll be consequences."
"The drop-off is at midnight, make sure you’re alone when you pick up the package."
"I don’t care who you need to hurt, just make sure the debt’s paid by tomorrow."
"The boss wants results, and if you can’t deliver, don’t bother showing up."
"I’ll take care of the hard part, just make sure you keep your mouth shut."
"Once we get the documents, it’s all over—we’ll be in the clear."
"You better have the product ready or we’ll find someone who can do the job."
"The authorities are closing in; we need to act fast before they catch on."
"Keep the conversation quiet, this isn’t something you want to get caught up in."
"If you’re not in by next week, we’ll have to find someone else to take care of business."
"I don’t care if it’s risky, just make sure the deal goes down without a hitch."
"If anyone sees us, the plan’s blown—keep your head down and follow the schedule."
"The package is in your hands now; don’t lose it, or we’re all in trouble."
"We’ve got a few hours before the authorities catch on—make sure everything’s in motion."
"The buyer’s waiting, so make sure the cash is ready and the delivery’s clean."
"Once this is done, we can all disappear—just make sure you don’t get caught."
"Don’t forget to burn the documents after you’re done; nothing can be traced back to us."
"The guard’s shift is over at 2 AM; we’ll move in then—everything’s set."
"The safehouse is secure; just keep your distance and don’t talk to anyone."
"I’ll handle the heavy lifting, you just make sure the car’s ready for the getaway."
"If you try to back out now, we’ll make sure you regret it."
"The payment’s been wired, just make sure the product’s in transit by tonight."
"It’s all set—just make sure no one finds out where it’s coming from."
"You need to move fast; they’ll be looking for you soon."
"We’re out of time; get the stuff to the buyer, or we’ll lose everything."
"I’ve got people on the inside, but if anything goes wrong, you’re on your own."
"If we can’t move this tonight, everything falls apart—get it done."
"You know the drill—don’t talk, don’t ask questions, just deliver."
"Once the money’s in, we’ll cut ties and disappear—no one will know what happened."
"You have one chance to get it right—if you screw this up, we’ll have a problem."
"The transfer’s been completed, just get the product to the client before anyone realizes it’s gone."
"Once we move the merchandise, the heat will die down—just keep it low-key."
"Get rid of the phone, the car, and everything else; we can’t leave traces behind."
"I’ll handle the front-end, you just focus on getting the goods out of there undetected."
"Don’t show your face, keep everything in cash—no one can know about this deal."
"You don’t have to ask questions, just deliver the package to the specified location and leave."
"We’ve got eyes everywhere; just don’t make a move until I give the signal."
"If the cops show up, we bail—don’t try to be a hero, just get out fast."
"The money’s wired; you need to move the shipment or we’ll have to find someone who can."
"Once the deal goes down, we’re cutting ties and disappearing—don’t leave anything behind."
"There’s a lot of risk in this, but the payoff’s worth it—just make sure the job gets done."
"Don’t let anyone follow you—if they do, I’ll handle it."
"We need the shipment by tonight, or we’ll lose the buyer."
"Get rid of the security cameras, we don’t want anyone watching this."
"If the package isn’t at the drop point by midnight, we’ll have to find someone else to finish the job."
"I’ve got the keys to the warehouse, but we need to get the goods before anyone arrives."
"We’ve been planning this for weeks—don’t mess it up now."
"You’ve got the documents, right? Make sure they’re destroyed before anyone sees them."
"The safe’s unlocked; just make sure the cash is gone before dawn."
"The buyer’s already waiting—move quickly, or we’ll lose the deal."
"Do you have the stuff ready? The buyer’s waiting."
"I need it by tomorrow, don’t make me wait, or we’ll have problems."
"We’ll meet at the usual spot. You know the time."
"Once we get the payment, the product will be shipped immediately."
"Make sure the packaging is secure—no one can know what’s inside."
"I’ll get the cash wired to you once I get the product."
"We need to finalize the deal before the authorities notice anything suspicious."
"Let’s meet at the warehouse for the exchange; I’ll bring the cash."
"We need to keep things low profile, no names, no traces."
"I’ve got the buyers lined up, but you need to deliver fast."
"The package is coming in—be sure to check the delivery when it lands."
"We’ll be moving the goods tonight—make sure everything’s secure."
"I need to pick up the new supplies by the end of the week."
"The shipment needs to be delivered to the warehouse; don’t forget the new arrangement."
"We’ll need to meet at the spot after dark to sort out the orders."
"Just make sure the job gets done by tomorrow night."
"Don’t worry, I’ve got everything under control with the arrangement."
"We’ll meet at the usual spot to finalize the details."
"Make sure the product gets delivered, and don’t ask too many questions."
"If you’re not able to make the move by then, we’ll have to find someone else who can."
"The account will be set up; just make sure the transfer is completed by tomorrow."
"The client is ready to pay, but we need to make sure the details are correct."
"You’ve got to keep this deal quiet for now—don’t tell anyone about the arrangements."
"The tools are packed and ready to go—just waiting for the right moment."
"Make sure to keep everything tight—no mistakes, no slip-ups."
"We’ll meet at the location to pick up the equipment—make sure it’s ready."
"There’s a shipment coming in; I need someone to move it quickly."
"Keep the cargo low profile, and don’t let anyone know what’s inside."
"Make sure the stuff gets to me by tonight—no delays."
"You got the bag ready for pickup?"
"The client wants the usual—nothing more, nothing less."
"I’ll take care of the transaction—just bring the money."
"The shipment needs to be moved ASAP before the authorities catch wind of it."
"I’ve got the goods ready. Just meet me at the usual spot after midnight."
"Can you handle the delivery tonight? The buyer is expecting it by morning."
"The product has to be delivered, no matter what. We don’t want to lose the deal."
"Check the package first to make sure everything is in order before sending it out."
"We can’t afford any mistakes—make sure everything is secured before the drop."
"I’ll bring the cash once I get the confirmation that the shipment went through."
"You need to keep everything clean, no names, no evidence."
"Make sure you get rid of all the materials after you’re done. We don’t want anything to link back."
"The route is clear, we can make the move tonight."
"You know what needs to be done, just make sure it’s taken care of by the end of the week."
"The job will go smoothly, as long as no one starts asking questions."
"We’ve got the team in place, just waiting for the green light."
"I’ll handle the dirty work, you just make sure the money is in the right hands."
"The deal is solid, but we need to keep everything low-profile until it's done."
"Let’s meet at the spot later to settle everything. No one can know we’re involved."
"I’ll make sure the product is moved quietly, we don’t need attention right now."
"The operation is in motion, just make sure everything is handled properly."
"We’ll split the take when everything is finished. Make sure no one gets caught."
"You’ll need to cover your tracks once you’re done—don’t leave any signs."
"I’ve got the laundry in progress, the funds will be cleaned soon."
"The wire transfer went through. Let’s move the money and get it out of the country."
"Once we get the funds into the system, everything should be good to go."
"You need to hide the source of the capital—no one can trace it back to us."
"The shell companies are set up; now we can funnel the cash through them."
"Once we convert the assets, it’ll be much harder for anyone to track."
"I’ll route the funds through multiple channels, just in case someone starts asking questions."
"We need to make sure the documents look clean for the auditors."
"I’ve set up the account for you to deposit the money. Just be quick about it."
"The exchange was successful—time to move the cleaned funds out of sight."
"The cargo is ready; just waiting on your call to move it."
"We need to make sure the shipment goes through without getting scanned."
"The container should arrive at the port tomorrow. Be ready to move it quickly."
"Get the transport set up to move the load to the new location tonight."
"Once the goods are on the truck, we’ll get them out of the country."
"I’ve secured the delivery point. Meet me there when the items arrive."
"We’ve got everything packed. The route is safe, but don’t take any chances."
"Check the logs and make sure everything’s in place before the cargo leaves."
"The stash needs to be moved as soon as possible—don’t let anyone see it."
"The package should be delivered directly to the buyer without any detours."
"The product is ready for pickup, just make sure the money is with you."
"The buyer is coming, make sure you have the right amount ready."
"I’ll meet you at the corner in 30 minutes; bring the cash."
"Let me know when you’re at the spot, I’ll have the stuff for you."
"Once the money comes through, the bag will be on its way."
"Don’t bring anyone with you; this has to stay between us."
"Make sure to keep the transaction quiet; no one can know about it."
"If anything goes wrong, just say you lost the bag—no one needs to know what happened."
"Get rid of the evidence after the deal, no one can trace it back to us."
"We can’t afford any mistakes this time, make sure you’re in and out quick."
"The items will be hidden in plain sight; just make sure you’re discreet."
"The route is mapped out; I’ll let you know when to move the shipment."
"Once the goods are inside the country, we’ll need to lay low for a while."
"Get the cargo ready for transport, but keep it under wraps—nothing flashy."
"The drop-off point is secured; we’ll move everything in the middle of the night."
"I’ll handle the paperwork, but you need to stay in touch about the delivery."
"You have the key to the warehouse, right? Get the items in tonight."
"Once the shipment arrives, we’ll be in business."
"We need to move the stuff quickly, so make sure the pickup is scheduled."
"No mistakes this time; if the shipment doesn’t go smoothly, we’re in deep trouble."
"I have the drugs ready for shipment. Where do you want them delivered?"
"I need to make the sale today. I’ll meet you at the usual place with the product."
"The buyer is expecting delivery tonight. How soon can you get the drugs to him?"
"The drugs are packed and ready to go. We just need to arrange a meeting point."
"How much are you charging for the drugs this time? I need to know before I make the purchase."
"We have a problem with the last shipment—half of it was intercepted. I need to fix this."
"The delivery didn’t go as planned. I need to make sure the next one goes through without issues."
"I’ve got a buyer lined up, but I’m short on supply. Can you get me more product today?"
"You need to handle the transportation carefully this time. If the authorities catch this shipment, it’s over."
"I’ll transfer the payment once I confirm the drugs have arrived at the location."
"I have the shipment of heroin ready to go. We just need to finalize the delivery details."
"The cocaine will be arriving tomorrow. Make sure you have the money when it gets here."
"We’re moving 100 kilos of methamphetamine this time. The buyer is waiting."
"I’ll send you the tracking number for the package. Make sure you’re ready to move the product once it arrives."
"The drugs are packed and sealed. I’ll meet you at the warehouse so we can unload them."
"The buyer is asking for a larger quantity this time. Can you handle the order?"
"Once we get the shipment through customs, we’ll need to distribute the drugs across the city."
"Make sure the drop goes smoothly tonight. If anyone sees us, we’re done."
"The money for the drugs needs to be delivered by the end of the day. Let me know when it’s ready."
"The deal’s going down tomorrow. Have the product ready and make sure everything is in order."
"The hit’s going down tonight. We need to make sure the target’s in the right place."
"We’re meeting with the rival gang at the bar to settle this. Bring the cash and the weapon."
"I’ve got everything set up for the heist. The target is a jewelry store, and we know where the goods are kept."
"You need to take care of the witness. No one can testify against us."
"Once we get the money, we’ll be out of town by morning. Make sure there are no problems."
"I’ve set up the alibi for all of us. No one will suspect a thing once we pull this off."
"The warehouse has been cleared. I’ll bring the product, and you bring the buyers."
"I’ll meet you at the docks with the guns. Make sure you have the cash when I get there."
"The target is set. We move at midnight. Don’t leave any trace behind."
"We can’t afford to get caught. Burn the evidence after the job."
"I’ve transferred the funds to the offshore account. We need to route the money through different companies to avoid suspicion."
"The real estate deal went through. I’ll get the cash for the property and move it into the next account."
"We need to make sure the fake invoices go through. Once they clear, we can move the money into the legitimate business accounts."
"I’ll move the money into the company’s account, then we’ll transfer it to multiple smaller accounts to make it harder to trace."
"The money is in the shell company. I’ll make sure the records show that the money came from a legitimate source."
"We need to clean this money quickly. Let’s buy and sell some expensive assets, then transfer the funds."
"I’ll route the money through the charity’s account. Once it’s there, it’ll be harder to track."
"I’ve set up a fake invoice to make it look like the money was payment for goods. Now we can move it."
"We need to make the company look legitimate. Buy some more assets to cover the transaction."
"The funds are in multiple accounts now. We can slowly move the money out without raising any alarms."
"The shipment of firearms will be arriving tomorrow. I need you to meet the truck at the port."
"We’ve got a buyer lined up for the guns. Make sure you don’t get caught transporting them."
"I’ll meet you at the warehouse with the guns. Make sure the coast is clear before I hand them over."
"The shipment’s delayed. We need to get the guns past customs without anyone noticing."
"The weapons are ready to go. We’ll need to make the exchange in the next few days."
"We need to change the route for transporting the weapons. The old one’s too risky now."
"Make sure the guns are hidden. I don’t want anyone searching the truck."
"The buyer wants the shipment now. I need you to coordinate the pickup and delivery."
"I’ve got a connection to move the firearms out of the country. We can’t afford any delays."
"The weapons are in the safehouse. I’ll arrange for the next shipment next week."
"I have the crack cocaine in stock. Do you want to pick it up now?"
"The buyer’s coming in 20 minutes. Make sure you’ve got the right amount of heroin for him."
"I’ll meet you at the park in 30 minutes with the product. Make sure the money’s ready."
"The dealer is coming to collect the cash. Don’t forget the amount we agreed on."
"I’ve got a new batch of ecstasy. I’ll sell it for $20 per pill."
"You need to be careful with this delivery. The cops have been patrolling the area."
"I’m running low on meth. Can you get more from the supplier tonight?"
"The buyer is asking for a larger order this time. Can you supply that amount?"
"I’ll bring the marijuana to you in the morning. Make sure you have the cash ready."
"Make sure you don’t get caught with the drugs. Keep everything on the low."
"The shipment of electronics is coming in. We need to get them past customs without getting caught."
"I’ve arranged for the contraband to be hidden in the containers. We’ll move it tonight."
"The goods are in the truck. Meet me at the warehouse to unload the shipment."
"We’ve got a large shipment of cigarettes coming in. I’ll take care of the paperwork."
"Make sure the guns are hidden with the merchandise. We can’t afford to have them seized at the border."
"The smuggled items need to be distributed immediately after they arrive. Can you coordinate the deliveries?"
"I’ve set up the route for the contraband. We’ll move it through the backroads to avoid any checkpoints."
"The shipment’s scheduled to arrive tomorrow. Get the trucks ready for the goods."
"Once the illegal items pass through customs, we’ll have to move quickly to deliver them."
"The smuggling route has been cleared. We just need to keep it under the radar."
"I’ve got a shipment of AK-47s coming in. We need to make sure the delivery goes smoothly."
"We’ll pick up the guns from the warehouse and make the transfer to the buyer tonight."
"I’ve arranged for the firearms to be shipped in parts. Once they arrive, we’ll assemble them."
"The weapons are in transit. I’ll meet you at the docks when they arrive."
"We’re smuggling the guns through the border crossing. I’ll make sure the paperwork is in order."
"Once the guns are in the country, we’ll need to move them to a secure location for distribution."
"The buyer’s ready for the delivery. Just make sure the goods are clean before the exchange."
"I’ve set up a meeting for the weapon transfer tomorrow. Make sure you have the cash ready."
"The firearms are hidden in the shipment. Let’s hope the customs agents don’t catch on."
"We’ll send the guns through a third-party vendor. They won’t know what’s inside."
"If you don’t pay up, we’ll have no choice but to hurt someone close to you."
"Don’t make me come after your family. You know I can get to them anytime."
"I’m warning you, don’t cross me again. Next time, it won’t be just a threat."
"If you report us, your life will be over. We know where you live."
"I’ll make sure you regret this. It’s not just business anymore, it’s personal."
"You don’t want to find out what happens if you mess with us. Consider this your final warning."
"I’ve got connections, and I can make things disappear. You don’t want to make me use them."
"If you don’t cooperate, I can guarantee that you’ll pay a heavy price."
"I’m not playing around. This is your last chance to get out clean."
"You better watch your back. If I see you around, it’ll be the last time."
"If you talk, we’ll make sure your reputation is ruined, no one will trust you again."
"You know what happens when people get in our way. You’re no different."
"We don’t need witnesses. If you see something, you better keep it to yourself."
"I’ll give you one chance to stay quiet. After that, we’ll have to take care of the problem."
"It’s simple—do what I say, and you walk away. Ignore the warning, and things get ugly."
"You don’t understand who you’re messing with. We’ll track you down if we have to."
"There’s no escape for people like you. You’re not as clever as you think."
"We don’t play nice when things go wrong. You don’t want to find out what happens next."
"I’ve already warned you. If you don’t back off, I’ll make sure there’s no coming back."
"One word from you, and your life as you know it will be over."
"We’ve been casing the joint for weeks. We know exactly when the guards switch shifts."
"Once we get inside, we’ll hit the vault first, then grab everything valuable in the office."
"The alarm system can be bypassed if we cut the right wires. I’ll handle the tech side of things."
"Let’s take out the cameras first, then we’ll work on getting the safe open."
"We need someone on the inside. It’s the only way we can avoid the high-tech security."
"I’ve already planned the getaway. We’ll be out of there in under 10 minutes."
"The layout of the building is simple, but we’ll need to keep an eye on the back entrance."
"Don’t forget—after we hit the bank, we’ll need to lay low for at least a week."
"We’ve got everything ready. We just need to make sure no one suspects anything before we make the move."
